creator: Myrtle Reed
description:
LibriVox recording of The Shadow of Victory by Myrtle Reed.
Read in English by Lynne Thompson; KHand; Natalie Paula; MaryAnn; crystalarmeta; Jairus Amar; Tony Green
This is another work by the author Myrtle Reed who is also the author of "The Spinster Bbook" and "Old Rose and Silver" and was a bestseller during 1903. (Summary by sidhu177)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
